"{\"uid\": \"scrippsnews.com-sports-paris-2024-olympics-olympic-boxing-champion-imane-khelif-filed-a-legal-complaint-for-online-harassment-against-her\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Olympic boxing champion Imane Khelif has filed a legal complaint in France for online harassment after a rain of criticism and false claims about her sex during the Paris Olympics, her lawyer said Sunday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 204, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 24, \"end\": 36, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421623295, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 68, \"end\": 74, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"score\": 0.7247317425063459, \"rank\": 0.3531047136154286, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Third_Republic\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a legal complaint\", \"from\": 47, \"to\": 64}, {\"ngram\": \"online harassment\", \"from\": 79, \"to\": 96}, {\"ngram\": \"a rain\", \"from\": 103, \"to\": 109}, {\"ngram\": \"criticism\", \"from\": 113, \"to\": 122}, {\"ngram\": \"false claims\", \"from\": 127, \"to\": 139}, {\"ngram\": \"her sex\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 153}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 161, \"to\": 179}, {\"ngram\": \"her lawyer\", \"from\": 181, \"to\": 191}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif, who will be Algeria's flag bearer in the closing ceremony, won gold Friday in the women's welterweight division, becoming a new hero in her native Algeria and bringing global attention to women's boxing.\", \"from\": 206, \"to\": 417, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 226, \"end\": 233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.999999997626901, \"rank\": 1.6734427277899036e-09, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 361, \"end\": 368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.999999997626901, \"rank\": 1.6734427277899036e-09, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 206, \"to\": 212}, {\"ngram\": \"the closing ceremony\", \"from\": 251, \"to\": 271}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 277, \"to\": 281}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's welterweight division\", \"from\": 292, \"to\": 325}, {\"ngram\": \"a new hero\", \"from\": 336, \"to\": 346}, {\"ngram\": \"global attention\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 398}, {\"ngram\": \"women's boxing\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 416}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The complaint was filed Friday with a special unit in the Paris prosecutor's office for combating online hate speech, alleging \\\"aggravated cyber-harassment\\\" targeting Khelif, lawyer Nabil Boudi said.\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 618, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 477, \"end\": 482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999996837232, \"rank\": 3.1623731167773626e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The complaint\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 432}, {\"ngram\": \"a special unit\", \"from\": 455, \"to\": 469}, {\"ngram\": \"online hate speech\", \"from\": 517, \"to\": 535}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 592}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a statement, he described it as a \\\"misogynist, racist and sexist campaign\\\" against the boxer.\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 715, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 633}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"misogynist, racist and sexist campaign\", \"from\": 654, \"to\": 695}, {\"ngram\": \"the boxer\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 714}]}, {\"sentence\": \"RELATED STORY |Olympic boxer Imane Khelif calls for end to bullying after backlash over gender misconceptions It is now up to prosecutors to decide whether to open an investigation.\", \"from\": 717, \"to\": 899, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 746, \"end\": 758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421623295, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"end\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 772}, {\"ngram\": \"backlash\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 799}, {\"ngram\": \"gender misconceptions\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 826}, {\"ngram\": \"prosecutors\", \"from\": 843, \"to\": 854}, {\"ngram\": \"an investigation\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 897}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As is common in French law, the complaint does not name an alleged perpetrator but leaves it to investigators to determine who could be at fault.\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 1045, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 916, \"end\": 926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_of_France\", \"score\": 0.9999797811258256, \"rank\": 1.9777789671527113e-05, \"text\": \"French law\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_of_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the complaint\", \"from\": 928, \"to\": 941}, {\"ngram\": \"an alleged perpetrator\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 978}, {\"ngram\": \"investigators\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1009}, {\"ngram\": \"fault\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1044}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif was unwittingly thrust into a worldwide clash over gender identity and regulation in sports after her first fight, whenItalian opponent Angela Carini pulled outjust seconds into the match, citing pain from opening punches.\", \"from\": 1047, \"to\": 1276, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1190, \"end\": 1203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103662667, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 1047, \"to\": 1053}, {\"ngram\": \"a worldwide clash\", \"from\": 1082, \"to\": 1099}, {\"ngram\": \"gender identity\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1120}, {\"ngram\": \"regulation\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1135}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1145}, {\"ngram\": \"her first fight\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1167}, {\"ngram\": \"whenItalian opponent\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1189}, {\"ngram\": \"outjust seconds\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1226}, {\"ngram\": \"the match\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1241}, {\"ngram\": \"pain\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1254}, {\"ngram\": \"punches\", \"from\": 1268, \"to\": 1275}]}, {\"sentence\": \"False claims that Khelif was transgender or a man erupted online, and the International Olympic Committee defended her and denounced those peddling misinformation.\", \"from\": 1277, \"to\": 1440, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1351, \"end\": 1382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"False claims\", \"from\": 1277, \"to\": 1289}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1301}, {\"ngram\": \"transgender\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1317}, {\"ngram\": \"a man\", \"from\": 1321, \"to\": 1326}, {\"ngram\": \"those peddling misinformation\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1439}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif said that the spread of misconceptions about her \\\"harms human dignity.\\\"\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1519, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1447}, {\"ngram\": \"the spread\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1468}, {\"ngram\": \"misconceptions\", \"from\": 1472, \"to\": 1486}, {\"ngram\": \"human dignity\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1517}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier, Kirsty Burrows, an official in charge of the IOC's unit for safeguarding and mental health, filed a complaint with French authorities saying she received death threats and harassment online following a news conference in Paris at which she had spoken in defense of Khelif.\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1802, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1575, \"end\": 1578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.915897691585985e-20, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1645, \"end\": 1651, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9979839848254699, \"rank\": 0.0012837999747641678, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1751, \"end\": 1756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999996837232, \"rank\": 3.1623731167773626e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kirsty Burrows\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1544}, {\"ngram\": \"an official\", \"from\": 1546, \"to\": 1557}, {\"ngram\": \"charge\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1567}, {\"ngram\": \"safeguarding\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1602}, {\"ngram\": \"mental health\", \"from\": 1607, \"to\": 1620}, {\"ngram\": \"a complaint\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1639}, {\"ngram\": \"death threats\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1697}, {\"ngram\": \"a news conference\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1747}, {\"ngram\": \"defense\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1791}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 1795, \"to\": 1801}]}, {\"sentence\": \"RELATED STORY |Lin Yu-ting of Taiwan clinches first Olympic medal amid outcry tied to gender misconceptions The Paris prosecutor's office said it received Burrows' complaint on Aug. 4 and agents from the National Unit for the Fight against Online Hate are investigating the alleged offenses, including death threats, public provocations aimed at attacking a person and cyberbullying.\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 2188, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1819, \"end\": 1830, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lin Yu-ting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\"}, {\"begin\": 1834, \"end\": 1840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"score\": 0.9999952281393856, \"rank\": 2.4946457111333265e-06, \"text\": \"Taiwan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\"}, {\"begin\": 1917, \"end\": 1922, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999996837232, \"rank\": 3.1623731167773626e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"RELATED STORY\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1817}, {\"ngram\": \"first Olympic medal\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 1869}, {\"ngram\": \"outcry\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1881}, {\"ngram\": \"gender misconceptions\", \"from\": 1890, \"to\": 1911}, {\"ngram\": \"Burrows' complaint\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 1977}, {\"ngram\": \"Aug.\", \"from\": 1981, \"to\": 1985}, {\"ngram\": \"agents\", \"from\": 1992, \"to\": 1998}, {\"ngram\": \"the National Unit\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2021}, {\"ngram\": \"the Fight\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2035}, {\"ngram\": \"Online Hate\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2055}, {\"ngram\": \"the alleged offenses\", \"from\": 2074, \"to\": 2094}, {\"ngram\": \"death threats\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2119}, {\"ngram\": \"public provocations\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2140}, {\"ngram\": \"a person\", \"from\": 2160, \"to\": 2168}, {\"ngram\": \"cyberbullying\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2186}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Under French law, the crimes, if proven, carry prison sentences that range from two to five years and fines ranging from 30,000 to 45,000 euros.\", \"from\": 2189, \"to\": 2333, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2195, \"end\": 2205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_of_France\", \"score\": 0.9999797811258256, \"rank\": 1.9777789671527113e-05, \"text\": \"French law\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_of_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the crimes\", \"from\": 2207, \"to\": 2217}, {\"ngram\": \"prison sentences\", \"from\": 2236, \"to\": 2252}, {\"ngram\": \"two to five years\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2286}, {\"ngram\": \"fines\", \"from\": 2291, \"to\": 2296}, {\"ngram\": \"30,000 to 45,000 euros\", \"from\": 2310, \"to\": 2332}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics-banned International Boxing Association disqualified Khelif and fellow boxer Lin Yu-ting of Taiwan from the world championships last year, claiming the two fighters failed unspecified eligibility tests for women's competition.\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2574, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2355, \"end\": 2387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.503800716638005e-21, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 2425, \"end\": 2436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lin Yu-ting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\"}, {\"begin\": 2440, \"end\": 2446, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"score\": 0.9999952281393856, \"rank\": 2.4946457111333265e-06, \"text\": \"Taiwan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 2401, \"to\": 2407}, {\"ngram\": \"fellow\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2418}, {\"ngram\": \"the world championships\", \"from\": 2452, \"to\": 2475}, {\"ngram\": \"the two fighters\", \"from\": 2496, \"to\": 2512}, {\"ngram\": \"unspecified eligibility tests\", \"from\": 2520, \"to\": 2549}, {\"ngram\": \"women's competition\", \"from\": 2554, \"to\": 2573}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC has called the arbitrary sex tests that the sport's governing body imposed on the two women irretrievably flawed and has defended both boxers since the start of the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 2575, \"to\": 2760, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2579, \"end\": 2582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.915897691585985e-20, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the arbitrary sex tests\", \"from\": 2594, \"to\": 2617}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport's governing body\", \"from\": 2623, \"to\": 2649}, {\"ngram\": \"the two women\", \"from\": 2661, \"to\": 2674}, {\"ngram\": \"both boxers\", \"from\": 2713, \"to\": 2724}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 2731, \"to\": 2740}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 2744, \"to\": 2759}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Experts say the scrutiny of Khelif and Lin reflected disproportionate scrutiny and discrimination toward female athletes of color when it comes to sex testing and false claims that they are male or transgender.\", \"from\": 2762, \"to\": 2972, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Experts\", \"from\": 2762, \"to\": 2769}, {\"ngram\": \"the scrutiny\", \"from\": 2774, \"to\": 2786}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 2790, \"to\": 2796}, {\"ngram\": \"Lin\", \"from\": 2801, \"to\": 2804}, {\"ngram\": \"disproportionate scrutiny\", \"from\": 2815, \"to\": 2840}, {\"ngram\": \"discrimination\", \"from\": 2845, \"to\": 2859}, {\"ngram\": \"female athletes\", \"from\": 2867, \"to\": 2882}, {\"ngram\": \"color\", \"from\": 2886, \"to\": 2891}, {\"ngram\": \"sex testing\", \"from\": 2909, \"to\": 2920}, {\"ngram\": \"false claims\", \"from\": 2925, \"to\": 2937}]}, {\"sentence\": \"About Scripps News\", \"from\": 2974, \"to\": 2992, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2980, \"end\": 2987, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/E._W._Scripps_Company\", \"score\": 0.782385425265201, \"rank\": 0.26820111981777534, \"text\": \"Scripps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/E._W._Scripps_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/E._W._Scripps_Company\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}]}"